How cute is this time of year! I love the small change Coca-Cola has recently made to their bottles by adding an attached cap! It’s easier to now keep the cap and bottle together so that you can throw the whole package in the recycling bin, and there’s no picking up stray bottle tops from the floor! This Christmas I’m really going HARD on minimising my waste. So I’ve thrown Rosie away and I’m drinking from the @cocacolaeu bottles with the new attached cap 😊 Small changes make a big difference ❤️ so together let’s start now x #AD  #CocaCola #attachedcaps

We had SO much fun at the Peppa Pig Discovery Playroom at the Natural History Museum! The theme of the pop up is sustainability and I'll tell you what else it sustained... ZIGGY'S ATTENTION! There are lots of different zones to keep your little one busy, the craft zone so you can take home cute drawings and a discovery zone where you can sit back and watch your favourite Peppa episodes. But best of all we MET @officialpeppa! Peppa will be there every Monday and it's running from the 5th August till the 10th September so RUN DON'T WALK! Bye for now! OINK @hasbro #ad
